text: Irina Shenberger (born 20 February 1992) is a Kazakhstani volleyball player. She played at the 2013 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2014 FIVB Women's World Championship, 2014 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2016 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for VC Astana. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani volleyball players
